Peter Bennett (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Bennett_(actor) 0 Peter Bennett (17 September 1917 – 23 December 1989) was a British stage and television actor. He had served on both the National Council for Drama Training and the British Actors' Equity Association.
